  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list><item>Identify the mathematical relationships between the various properties of gases</item>
<item>Use the ideal gas law, and related gas laws, to compute the values of various gas properties under specified conditions</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:language>en</md:language>
